OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry start
OL,6,Fto the evening then a band of rain
OL,7,Fcrossing Orkney mid evening then
OL,8,FShetland around midnight, followed by
OL,9,Fclearer weather with scattered
OL,10,Fshowers. Southerly gales.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FShowers will become more
OL,13,Ffrequent during the morning, then more
OL,14,Fscattered later with more in the way
OL,15,Fof sunshine. Strong to gale southerly
OL,16,Fwinds veering westerly, perhaps severe
OL,17,Fbriefly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
