OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,6,Fvery showery few days the showers most
OL,7,Ffrequent and heavy on Thursday when
OL,8,Fthere will be southwesterly gales.
